All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, java.rmi.Remote, Computer2Space
public class ComputerProxy
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements java.lang.Runnable, Computer2Space

Represents a thread taking tasks from the Space and sends it to the registered computers to execute it remotely and place the Result back into the Space to be fetched by the clients.

Author:
Vijayaraghavan Subbaiah
